00:45:22.180 --> 00:45:25.249
we're going to do a little
"Circle of Life," I think.

00:45:25.249 --> 00:45:27.540
What do y'all think, y'all
ready to do a little "Circle

00:45:27.540 --> 00:45:27.970
of Life?"

00:45:27.970 --> 00:45:28.800
Think we could do that.

